<ab facs="#facs_198_r2l6">ſein ſülle / Nu hat der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vor vns cʒu den </ab>
