</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_198" id="98v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>B<ex>er</ex>nhart</expan>, <expan>herczog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>zu</add> Prawnsweig und zu <expan>Lünenb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Conrad Kresse, unser
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, von seinen und
                                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> gesellschafft, auch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wegen, wie daz im
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> aufgehalten hab ein veszlein mit
                                <expan>schöne<ex>m</ex></expan> werck, <add>daz in
                                    <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rephun, ir
                                <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, herausz gesant hab</add>, und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade main, daz das der von Lübeck sein
                        sülle. Nu hat der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vor uns czu den
                            <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt, daz das
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> veszlein mit
                                <expan>schone<ex>m</ex></expan> werk sein und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> sey, also daz <expan>khein<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        von Lübek noch sust khein auszman daran weder teil noch gemaine hab.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>unsre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab on hindernüsse
                            <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen wölle. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>sex<ex>ta</ex></expan> ante Lucie
                        <expan>virg<ex>inis</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
